title: Give me a new summoner name for the new year!
body:
I main Quinn in all 3 lanes, so I'm mainly looking for something that refrences that. I also play support regularly, so it could be about that too (inb4 IGetCarried.) Please make it funny or interesting, I'm spending a lot of IP on this.

EDIT: Thanks everyone! I decided to go with Quinntuple Kill, but it was a difficult choice, since there were so many awesome suggestions.
